.TH XGetXCBConnection 3 "libX11 1.6.1" "X Version 11" "XLIB FUNCTIONS"
.SH NAME
XGetXCBConnection \- git tha XCB connection fo' a Xlib Display
.SH SYNTAX
.HP
 #include <X11/Xlib-xcb.h>
.HP
xcb_connection_t *XGetXCBConnection(Display *\fIdpy\fP); 
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP \fIdpy\fP 1i
Specifies tha connection ta tha X server.
.SH DESCRIPTION
Da \fIXGetXCBConnection\fP function returns tha XCB connection associated with
an Xlib Display.  Clients can use dis XCB connection wit functions from the
XCB library, just as they would wit a XCB connection pimped wit XCB.
Callaz of dis function must link ta libX11-xcb n' a version of Xlib built
with XCB support.
